title: J Mascis x Kim Gordon – “Slow Boy” (OFFICIAL AUDIO STREAM)
description:
“Slow Boy” is the second single off of the third Converse CONS compilation, CONS EP Vol. 3, with two more tracks being released throughout June 2015. The song was written by J Mascis and Kim Gordon, with Mascis handling production as well.

Music by: J Mascis & Kim Gordon
Written by: J Mascis & Kim Gordon
Vocals by: Kim Gordon
Mixed by: J Mascis and Mark Alan Miller at Bisquiteen
Mastered by: Mark Alan Miller at Sonelab
